                <div>
                        <h2>Dr. Lawrence "Larry" Stanleigh (Southern Alberta)</h2>
                        <p>Dr. Larry Stanleigh BSc MSc DDS FADI FICD, is a graduate of the University of Toronto Faculty of Dentistry. He operates a large general practice in the Mission area of Calgary, with a special interest in Gneuromuscular dentistry, Cosmetic dentistry, Facial pain and Sports Dentistry. A member of several organizations, including the Canadian Dental Association, Academy of General Dentistry, Occlusion Connections, American Academy of Cosmetic Dentistry, Academy of Laser Dentistry, the Academy of Sports Dentistry, and more, Dr. Larry strives to bring balance, comprehensive care and fun to his practice, his patients and his life.<br>An avid runner, bicyclist, skier, golfer, Dr. Larry understands the needs of the athlete, both professional and recreational. Dr. Stanleigh is located at &nbsp;1800 4 St SW, Suite 1601, Calgary	Alberta T2V 4Y1 .  <strong>Phone:&nbsp;(403) 228-3783. &nbsp;Email: &nbsp;drstanleigh@agilityguard.com</strong>
