                <div>
                      <h2>Dr.Janish Grewal (Northern Caribbean)</h2>
                      <p>Dr. Janish Singh Grewal BDS MDCH, a resident of the Cayman Islands, is a member of the General Dental Council (UK) and Medical and Dental Council (Cayman). He obtained a  Bachelors of Dental Surgery from the University of Dundee (UK) in 1997. Prior to working in the Cayman Islands, Dr. Grewal was in private practice (2000-2009) in London, where he had extensive experience in Dental Occlusion, reconstructive dentistry and treating patients who suffer from pain associated with the head and neck. He concentrated on this area of Dentistry by completing a number of training programs in the UK and Las Vegas - specifically in Neuromuscular dentistry at  the Las Vegas Institute during 2005-2008, returning in 2010 to continue on his previous teachings with Dr. Clayton Chan at the Occlusion Connections. Dr. Grewal has also completed a Medical diploma in clinical hypnosis from the University of Greenwich (UK). In his spare time he enjoys playing golf, watersports and going to the gym.&nbsp;Dr Grewal's office is located Seven Mile Beach Dental Clinic, Marquee Plaza, Seven Mile Beach, Grand Cayman, Cayman Islands. T<strong>elephone: 1 345 943 7400 (office). &nbsp;Email: &nbsp;drgrewal@agilityguard.com</strong>
                      </p>
