                <div>
                      <h2><strong>Dr. Nathalie Vachon (Quebec)</strong>
                      </h2>
                      <p>Graduated from the Laval University, Faculty of Dentistry in 1990.  A firm believer in ongoing education, she has continued to pursue advanced post-graduate training with over 350 hours of continuing education annually primarily in the areas of cosmetic dentistry, orthodontics and cranio-mandibular disorders.</p>
                      <p>Dr. Vachon is currently in the process of completing a post-graduate Certificate of Esthetic Dentisry through the University of Minnesota. She is an active member of the American Academy of Cosmetic Dentistry as well as several other esteemed advanced training and dental associations including:</p>
                      <p>•	Occlusion Connections<br>•	American Academy of Craniofacial Pain<br>•	Academy of General Dentistry<br>•	International Association of Orthodontics <br>•	Las Vegas Institute<br>•	Ordre des Dentistes du Québec<br>•	Association des Chirurgiens Dentistes du Québec</p>
                      <p>Dr. Vachon is located at 2960 Becancour, Lyster, Quebec G0S 1V0  <strong>Phone : 819 389-5755 </strong>
