                <div>
                      <h2><strong>Dr. Arthur "Art" Kwan (Northern California)</strong>
                      </h2>
                      <p>Arthur S. Kwan, DMD is a 1996 graduate of Boston University Goldman School of Dentistry. He has been featured in numerous media publications, such as New Beauty magazine, Sacramento Magazine, KXTV Sacramento News 10, and KTXL Fox 40, where he has shared his insights about the most current cosmetic dentistry trends, techniques and performance enhancing mouth guard technology.&nbsp;</p>
                      <p>Dr. Kwan has incorporated neuromuscular concepts in his practice since 2003 to better his patient's lives and continually engages in continuing education for his patients' benefit. He is a member of the AACD. He has enjoys being part of the education arena teaching other dentists CAD / CAM dentistry. He and his wife, Dr. Sally Hsu, maintain a practice in Rocklin, California with a focus on comprehensive adhesive based dentistry including full mouth rehabilitation and TMJ disorders.&nbsp;</p>
                      <p>Recently, Dr. Kwan has delved deeper into continuing education at Occlusion Connections to increase the standard of care for his patients and to Optimize his athlete's performance incorporating AgilityGuard. &nbsp;</p>
                      <p>Dr. Kwan is located at 2230 Sunset Blvd., Suite 370, Rocklin, California &nbsp;95765. &nbsp;<strong>Phone: 916 780-9688 &nbsp;</strong>Website: www.WeMakeSacrametoSmile.com</p>
                </div>
